In this assignment (P1 Aligntext), I separate the project into 2 classes :
- AlignText : the entry of the project
- TextProcessor : the class contains main functionality, has 2 methods :
	1. parse : read input file, process all the input lines so that each line's length not exceeds the maximum char length permitted
	2. printFormated : display the parse result based on mode selected.

Compile :
- in the directory contains all the files 
- javac AlignText.java (will automatically compile FileUtil and TextProcessor)

Run : 
- java AlignText [input file path] [maxline length] [mode]